{"tid":1053622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★考古學！香港metoo個案，最勁追數58年（1961年）","createTime":"2019-03-09T08:09:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T14:25:50.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9435629b2498c2593e8b48f3ef5aec3b797d9d2e","tid":1053622,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T08:09:41.000Z","msg":"反性侵性騷擾運動#Me Too風潮近年席捲全球，各地都有女性勇敢挺身舉報遭受侵犯的經歷，惟有調查發現香港性暴力受害人平均延遲13.2年始求助！為性暴力受害人提供支援的團體「風雨蘭」發表2000年至2018年期間深入跟進的3611宗性暴力求助個案，發現強姦、非禮及性騷擾個案均呈現上升趨勢，逾20%受害人案發時未滿16歲，逾80%侵犯者與受害人相識，受害人延遲求助的情況普遍，<span style=\"color: red;\">最嚴重的個案延遲時間達58年之久</span>。研究認為司法系統未能有效回應受害者的實際需要，促政府優化支援受害人服務。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190309/bkn-20190309110225169-0309_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190309%2Fbkn-20190309110225169-0309_00822_001.html&d=i2Kzi6k%2Bo1XjTd2IKJX6ubccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=3fd880f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190309/bkn-20190309110225169-0309_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"086339a54b9cfc1478633ddc2828d6525486cf4d","tid":1053622,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T08:10:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190309/photo/bkn-20190309110225169-0309_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190309135517\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190309%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190309110225169-0309_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190309135517&h=ed1d2efd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fa02a9d7ee6277349a16be8739422a80eef6b9d3","tid":1053622,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T08:10:24.000Z","msg":"有冇<br />\n1941-1945？"},{"pid":"8980b8bb87accbabc15891556f8dd7354a8364e0","tid":1053622,"uid":135408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T08:16:31.000Z","msg":"李偲嫣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" clas